<h2 class="c-cover__title">
<span class="c-cover__title__body">The great medicines migration</span>
<span class="c-cover__title__foot">How China took control of key global pharmaceutical supplies</span>
</h2><p class="c-cover__date">April 5, 2022</p><p class="c-cover__link"><a class="c-en-link" href="https://vdata.nikkei.com/newsgraphics/chinavaccine-3/">Read in japanese</a></p></div></div><div class="c-cover__img">
<div class="c-cover__img__wrap">
<picture>
<source srcset="img/main_v_pc.png" media="(min-width: 580px)">
<img src="img/main_v_sp.png" alt="Key illustration">
</picture>
</div></div></div><div class="l-rail">
<p class="c-cover__lead">By the pandemic year of 2020, China accounted for the bulk of exports of certain pharmaceutical raw materials. The country now plays an indispensable role in the supply chain for antibiotics and vitamins.</p></div><div class="l-rail l-rail--m" id="sc-anchor1">
<div class="c-cover__magic-num">
<div class="c-cover__magic-num__title-wrap">
<div class="l-rail l-rail--full">
<h4 class="t-headline4 c-cover__magic-num__title">China’s share of global exports of key pharmaceutical ingredients in 2020, by volume</h4></div></div><div class="c-cover__magic-num__wrap" id="tet_dox">
<p class="c-cover__magic-num__head">Tetracycline/Doxycycline</p><div class="c-cover__magic-num__body">
<div class="c-cover__magic-num__chart">
<div class="c-cover__magic-num__chart__value" style="height:0%"></div></div><p class="c-cover__magic-num__value">
