</p></div></div><div class="c-cover__magic-num__wrap" id="aspi">
<p class="c-cover__magic-num__head">Aspirin</p><div class="c-cover__magic-num__body">
<div class="c-cover__magic-num__chart">
<div class="c-cover__magic-num__chart__value" style="height:0%"></div></div><p class="c-cover__magic-num__value">
